title: KnittingPattern
position: -349,-228
---
//(It's a pdf with a tutorial for knitting a hat with cat ears.)
<<setCanClick DocumentIcon_2 false>>

Anna: Oh! I wanted to make those for carnival last year.
Anna: One for me and one for Dana.
Anna: She said we would look ridiculous. (She laughs.)
Anna: We ended up not going. I don't need the pattern anymore.
Camille: We can leave this one for later, if you want.
Anna: You are kind. But I think we should delete it.

<<startPulsating CloseButtonPattern>>
<<startPulsatingFile DocumentIcon_2>>
<<setCanDrag DocumentIcon_2 true>>

