title: Drink
position: -349,-228
---

<<ZoomOutCamera>>
Anna: Thank you. I'm sorry you're spending your time deleting files instead of studying or enjoying your free time.
Camille: Oh, no problem.
// I'm letting you work now.
Anna: Would you like something to drink?
Anna: Coffee? Tea? I also have those terrible little biscuits my grandson loves.

-> Coffee would be nice, thank you.
    Anna: Good. People work better with a little bit of fuel, especially my coffee!
    <<ZoomOutCamera>>
    <<jump AloneAtDesktop>>
-> No, thank you. I should continue. // TODO: Should we add points when she's gentle or not ?
    Anna: Serious student! Don't let me distract you.
    Anna: I will be in the kitchen if you need me.
    <<jump AloneAtDesktop>>
-> Maybe later.
    Anna: Alright!
    <<jump AloneAtDesktop>>

