title: AloneAtDesktop
---
//(You can hear Anna walking away.)

//(You are still facing Anna's desktop.)

//(A NOTIFICATION alerting Anna that her inbox is full appears at the corner of the screen.)
//(The mailbox icon is GLOWING.)

<<activateObject DesktopScreen>>
<<startPulsatingFile MailFullNotification>>

Camille: hmmm...

-> Open the mailbox.
    <<jump Mailbox>>
-> Keep working on the desktop.
    <<jump Desktop>>

